<hymn_number>224</hymn_number>
<title>Jerusalem Thak</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chunglam Jerusalem thak khu,
 Mi thiengthote khawpi ahi;
 Belam No Lal Immanuel in vai a hawm,
 Matieng Zion gam nuom chu mu bang ka ngai.

[V2]
 Nuoi simlei mun sangin a nuomzawi kumsawt gam chu
 Sun ni cheng in mi zatam in sihsiel bang a zuon ui
 Zion tang chunga Belam No zaila'n a chawian ui

[V3]
 2. Immanuel Na thisan chu,
 Ka kumsawt zaila ding ahi;
 Mi thiengtho gam ka tun tieng zaila tuoilo sa'n,
 Kumsawt tuolthing Lal nunnem lim bel tang ie.

[V4]
 3. Hallelujah Aw Hukdampa,
 Sietlei thangvan Nang a ahiu,
 Na thisan lun in nei tan tai, Nanga ka hiu,
 Ka hun ngak buoina Jordan mei zing nuoi ah.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa, Na hung ding a nai tam?
 Sietlei lungkham meipi'n a bawm
 Kanaan gam leh Na sakmel ngaih a hai thei puoi,
 Zing tha pu'n khuo thiengtho a len ka nuom ie.</lyrics>
</song>